Now here’s where I think your metaphor becomes more than a metaphor.

Water follows gradients.

Pressure.

Gravity.

Temperature.

Chemical potential.

Ideas seem to follow different gradients.

Attention.

Need.

Curiosity.

Power.

Beauty.

Utility.

Trust.

Those aren’t physical gradients, but they influence how ideas spread through societies. People, institutions, and technologies create channels that make some ideas easier to transmit than others.

